10:39.120 --> 10:41.120
 Well, I think if you think about

10:41.120 --> 10:44.440
 sort of the early stages of development in infancy,

10:44.440 --> 10:45.920
 certainly that is true.

10:45.920 --> 10:48.760
 You're kind of born with probably

10:48.760 --> 10:50.280
 whatever is your baseline level,

10:50.280 --> 10:54.600
