11:06.280 --> 11:08.360
 or easily excited,

11:08.360 --> 11:10.240
 these are, I think, about the kind of people where you say,

11:10.240 --> 11:12.200
 hey, do you want to check out this new place for tacos?

11:12.200 --> 11:13.400
