11:16.640 --> 11:19.280
 harder to budge, like my bulldog Costello.

11:20.600 --> 11:23.200
 Very, very stable low levels of dopamine

11:23.200 --> 11:24.960
 with big inflections in his case.

11:27.360 --> 11:31.660
 Do you think that's set in terms of our parents

11:31.660 --> 11:34.960
 and obviously nature and nurture interact,

11:34.960 --> 11:39.080
