13:30.680 --> 13:32.320
 Is that related to impulsivity

13:32.320 --> 13:35.100
 or is what you're referring to an attempt

13:35.100 --> 13:38.880
 to withhold behavior that's very deliberate

13:38.880 --> 13:40.480
